        description: "Dear users,\nWe have another update regarding the CEDA Archive data incident that occurred on 18th November 2025. Please read the key points below:\n",
        
        
        content: "Dear users,\nWe have another update regarding the CEDA Archive data incident that occurred on 18th November 2025. Please read the key points below:\nNew data is now starting to be deposited into the Archive. We have restored the Archives skeleton directory structure. This means ~70% of the archive is now available again. For data recovery, we are going to prioritise popular datasets and data that is more integral to the structure of the Archive in the first instance. We have compiled a list of common questions - please take a look at this. Please bear with us during this time; it will be a lengthy and complex process, and we anticipate further obstacles down the road.\nWe appreciate your patience and understanding.\nThe CEDA Team"
