        description: "Dear JASMIN users,\nThis message includes information about the following:\nNew high-memory CentOS7 sci machines Retiring RHEL6 high-mem Sci machines on Friday 25th September Hpxfer servers Details of the update \u0026nbsp; The new high-memory (1TB) CentOS7 scientific analysis server with SLURM enabled sci3.jasmin.ac.uk and sci6.jasmin.ac.ukandsci8.jasmin.ac.uk are available for users to use\n",
        
        
